{
  "texts": [
    "The search terms were as follows: (Breast Cancer AND (Nursing OR Diagnosis AND Treatment OR Rehabilitation OR Traditional Chinese Medicine OR Guidelines OR Textbooks)).",
    "We utilized the BGE model 17, a free and open-source pretrained model that supports both Chinese and English vector embeddings, for the RAG-GPT group.",
    "Initially, breast cancer knowledge-based texts obtained in the previous step were sliced into paragraphs.",
    "Each paragraph was vectorized using the BGE model to create a vector retrieval database.",
    "The RAG model was configured using a cosine similarity threshold of 0.8."
  ]
}